            <p class="text-dark-400 dark:text-light-400 text-sm">Each project follows a structured yet adaptable process that ensures quality, meets deadlines, and delivers exceptional value. Below are the key phases of my development methodology:</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-light-200 dark:bg-dark-300 rounded-lg p-5 transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.03]">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mr-3">
