              <li>• User research & persona development</li>
              <li>• Requirements gathering</li>
              <li>• Technical feasibility assessment</li>
              <li>• Project roadmap creation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-light-200 dark:bg-dark-300 rounded-lg p-5 transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.03]">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mr-3">
                <span class="font-bold">2</span>
              </div>
              <h5 class="font-bold">Design & Architecture</h5>
            </div>
