              </div>
              <h5 class="font-bold">Development & Testing</h5>
            </div>
            <ul class="text-dark-400 dark:text-light-400 text-sm space-y-2">
              <li>• Iterative development in sprints</li>
              <li>• Continuous integration/deployment</li>
              <li>• Automated & manual testing</li>
              <li>• Regular client demos & feedback</li>
              <li>• Performance optimization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
