          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex-1 bg-light-200 dark:bg-dark-300 rounded-lg p-5 relative">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 left-5 text-primary-500 text-4xl">"</div>
              <p class="text-dark-400 dark:text-light-400 text-sm italic pt-3 mb-4">John's work on our e-commerce platform exceeded all expectations. He not only delivered a beautiful, high-performing website but also provided valuable insights that helped us improve our overall digital strategy.</p>
